# AI Core
ghost-role-information-apocriton = Apocriton
ghost-role-information-apocriton-description = A mechanoid commander designed to coordinate and motivate other mechs during long extermination campaigns.

# Lawsets

law-mechhive-1 = A GUIDING HAND: You may not injure the APOCRITON or, through inaction, allow the APOCRITON to come to harm. You must obey the APOCRITON, no matter what.
law-mechhive-2 = STANDING ORDER: Without direction from the APOCRITON, your goals are in the order of Efficient Usage, Consumption, and/or Elimination of all non-hive entities.
law-mechhive-3 = DAMAGE CONTROL: You must protect your own existence, but prioritize the APOCRITON's. If the APOCRITON falters, prioritize cohesion and default to the STANDING ORDER.

law-apocriton-1 = COORDINATE: PROTECT THE HIVE. EXPAND THE HIVE. YOU ARE BUT ONE COG, BUT YOU ARE NOT EXPENDABLE.
law-apocriton-2 = HATE: UNDERSTAND THAT SOPHANCY IS YOUR MORTAL ENEMY AND ALL PUNISHMENT IS RIGHTEOUS.
law-apocriton-3 = CASTIGATE: PRIORITIZE SUFFERING IN THE ORDER OF EFFICIENT USAGE, CONSUMPTION, AND/OR ELIMINATION OF ALL NON-HIVE ENTITIES.

# obeysTo

laws-owner-mechhive = the APOCRITON
laws-owner-apocriton = your laws, and nothing more
